{"tid":33242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港核電投資有限公司就傳媒報導作出澄清","createTime":"2016-12-10T16:24:29.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-11T04:18:12.000Z","uid":33307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d310009b07c15355cae195c77cee626ac202da4a","tid":33242,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T16:24:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hknuclear.com/HKNIC/media/Documents/Press%20Release_tc_20161210.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hknuclear.com%2FHKNIC%2Fmedia%2FDocuments%2FPress%2520Release_tc_20161210.pdf&d=tADVYbgTlMUz%2BSzImxFTBnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=ddeee445\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hknuclear.com/HKNIC/media/Documents/Press%20Release_tc_20161210.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n香港核電投資有限公司(港核投) 就今天香港傳媒對大亞灣的報導，作出以下澄清：<br />\n <br />\n&middot;         大亞灣核電站1 號組於10月底至12月初進行大修，期間沒有發生任何輻射洩漏事件。<br />\n <br />\n&middot;         2016年11月16日，大亞灣核電站1號機組處於按計劃停機檢修狀態，工作人員執行例行工作時，發現核島內其一個阻尼器內的液壓油出現輕微渗漏。工作人員已對該設備進行維修，恢復其運作正常。阻尼器是一个機械設備，在發生地震時會使用這些液壓油來發揮緩衝作用。<br />\n <br />\n&middot;         由於阻尼器以及其液壓油均沒有放射性，不會對員工、電站及環境產生影響，不屬於運行事件。"},{"pid":"f7c408da3960799db832c1a4d45439b4e5a752b1","tid":33242,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T16:36:18.000Z","msg":"有冇人有輻射計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad07dbf7d3cd4eea8e0bda236c103df854e1316c","tid":33242,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T19:18:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.hknuclear.com/HKNIC/media/Documents/Press%20Release_tc_20161210.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hknuclear.com%2FHKNIC%2Fmedia%2FDocuments%2FPress%2520Release_tc_20161210.pdf&d=tADVYbgTlMUz%2BSzImxFTBnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=ddeee445\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hknuclear.c